			<tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">it is possible to win against attackers 2x your power, or atleast defend yourself and prevent planets from being sieged.  Just have multiple windows with preset defence plans which you can make up during the 10 min cooldown for declare.  What you wanna aim to do is have your main fleet on defence when they attack with scout fleets, or small ammount of ships, and have cloaked cruisers on defense when they send out their main fleets.  After they encounter your Cloaked cruisers, they will no doubt try to send cloak detection fleets to kil em off.  Just put your main ships on defence when they do.  To time it right, just keep refreshing war screen and checking bports as to what their sending at you.  People will as you sed, usualy send a scout and then attack with a large portion of ships which they judge would be enough to kill your ships.
<br />
It's a cheap tactic, but it works if you can time it all right.  Besides, their already being cheap by attacking someone half their power.<br />_________________<br /><img src="http://img154.imageshack.us/img154/8413/georgedance7ne.gif" border="0" /></span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
